lass=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kno1665703133480.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kno1665703133480.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kno1665703133480.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kno1665703133480\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"kno1665703133480__uputregf_408572\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy a double-precision floating-point value into the specified general variable ($1\n      ... $99).</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kno1665703133480__topic_d123773e1_d123774e1_d123775e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104kno1665703133480_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kno1665703133480__codeblock_fz3_xgk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long uputregf (shortregNbr, doublevalue);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665703133480__topic_d87437e1_d87438e1_d87439e1_d87440e1_d87441e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d414070e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"kno1665703133480__parml_a4t_ygk_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">regNbr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Number of the Uniface general variable. This must be from 1 to 99.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Double-precision floating point value to put into the general variable.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665703133480__topic_d87442e1_d87443e1_d87444e1_d87445e1_d87446e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d414070e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kno1665703133480__p_d123791e1_d123792e1_d123793e1\">0—<code class=\"ph codeph\">uputregf</code> always returns zero.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665703133480__topic_d87447e1_d87448e1_d87449e1_d87450e1_d87451e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d414070e102\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kno1665703133480__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665703133480__topic_d87452e1_d87453e1_d87454e1_d87455e1_d87456e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d414070e115\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kno1665703133480__p_d123803e1_d123804e1_d123805e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uputregf</code> copies the\n            double-precision floating-point <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var> to the Uniface general variable\n            (also known as dollar register) with the specified number <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var>,\n            which can range from 1 to 99. There is no check on the validity of\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var>; if it is out of range, a crash is likely to result.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kno1665703133480__p_d123806e1_d123807e1_d123808e1\">Note that the precision of a <code class=\"ph codeph\">double</code> value is system-dependent, and might not match the 24-digit internal precision of Uniface. You might see truncation or rounding problems when you use too many significant digits. Uniface will always format general variables with double values in scientific format, even if <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var> is not.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104kno1665703133480_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kno1665703133480__codeblock_olr_chk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nEXPORT long putdoubles ()\n{\nuputregf(1, -1.23E-10);\n/* $1 is displayed in Uniface as -1.23000000000000e-010 */\nuputregf(2, 4.5678E20);\n/* $2 is displayed in Uniface as 4.56780000000000e+020 */\nuputregf(3, 123.456);\n/* $3 is displayed in Uniface as 1.23456000000000e+002 */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyf1665703133267.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ugetregf</a><p>Get the double-precision value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wrj1665703133411.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uputreg</a><p>Copy a long integer value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vdw1665703133550.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uputregs</a><p>Copy a string value to the specified general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529298\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529298\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uputregf Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Copy a double-precision floating-point value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). Explain this code long uputregf (shortregNbr, doublevalue); Copy Parameters regNbr Number of the Uniface general variable. This must be from 1 to 99. value Double-precision floating point value to put into the general variable. Return Values 0— uputregf always returns zero. Use Library: yrtl Description uputregf copies the double-precision floating-point value to the Uniface general variable (also known as dollar register) with the specified number value , which can range from 1 to 99. There is no check on the validity of value ; if it is out of range, a crash is likely to result. Note that the precision of a double value is system-dependent, and might not match the 24-digit internal precision of Uniface. You might see truncation or rounding problems when you use too many significant digits. Uniface will always format general variables with double values in scientific format, even if value is not. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT long putdoubles () { uputregf(1, -1.23E-10); /* $1 is displayed in Uniface as -1.23000000000000e-010 */ uputregf(2, 4.5678E20); /* $2 is displayed in Uniface as 4.56780000000000e+020 */ uputregf(3, 123.456); /* $3 is displayed in Uniface as 1.23456000000000e+002 */ } Copy Related Links ugetregf Get the double-precision value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99). uputreg Copy a long integer value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). uputregs Copy a string value to the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}